<plot>A short in the "Melody Master Bands" series from Warners that opens in Cuba where Carlos Molina discovers a group of native musicians playing such instruments as bongos timbales, clave, maracas and guajiro. Lydia Vendrell sings/chants "Chiqua-Chi", the band plays "Rhumba Rhapsody" and "Nague" and dancers Teddy Rodrigue &amp; Phyllis do a turn.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?382410</url></doc>
